{"tid":1822760,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"以後除咗「和理影」，仲可以加多個「和理問」，一齊測試藍色快餐店服務指數！","createTime":"2020-01-13T07:00:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-13T07:21:47.000Z","uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"69436b18f6be0ab32bd6df3b26e983c9a1e8e704","tid":1822760,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T07:00:08.000Z","msg":"做得藍絲港豬多數都有以下特徵：<br />\n臉皮厚過地殼<br />\n萬事利益為先<br />\n凡事捨難取易<br />\n服從權威人士<br />\n放棄邏輯思維<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n哩班人你想用影大頭方式令佢驚？唔好意思，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>係佢地嘅人生裡面「尊嚴」從來都排係「著數」同「方便」後面</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n舉個例，如果吉野家宣佈畀你地影幾張相就可以免費換一碗牛汁狗飯，條隊一定會長到過海兼且有人會重複排幾次<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再加上佢地平時只會群係藍色圈子裡面，<span style=\"color: red;\">你想杯都未必杯到</span>，哩一點大家係上幾次罷工應該已經感受過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以我想講嘅係，與其諗點樣畀壓力藍絲，不如認真諗下點樣<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">畀麻煩藍絲</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例如經常係食飯時間一大班人排隊，問一大輪野之後<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔食</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第一個測試對象肯定係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">吉野家</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n認同請推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"441b941bd1b47e03dc5965d64432dd6789d113ca","tid":1822760,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T07:11:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce72d96752b8f975604903d80d1d7b373a972f87","tid":1822760,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"441b941bd1b47e03dc5965d64432dd6789d113ca","tid":1822760,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T07:11:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T07:21:47.000Z","msg":"咁留意我做乜呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n擺低粒膠又唔講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}